# IntellMeet — AI-Powered Enterprise Meeting Platform

A full-stack meeting intelligence platform with real-time video, AI summaries via Google Gemini, Socket.io live chat, and a Kanban action item tracker.

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | React 18 + Vite 5 + Tailwind CSS v3 |
| Backend | Node.js + Express 4 |
| Database | MongoDB Atlas + Mongoose |
| Auth | JWT (jsonwebtoken) + bcryptjs |
| Real-time | Socket.io |
| AI | Google Gemini API (`gemini-1.5-flash`) |

